        "body": "## Summary\n\nFixes an unrelated `check-dependencies` CI failure from https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/actions/runs/26864214240/job/79224291792?pr=89701.\n\nThe failed job was `pnpm deadcode:unused-files`, which reported the agent-local SQLite cache/database files as unexpected unused files. This removes that unused production surface, drops its generated schema/type entry, removes the raw-SQL guardrail allowlist entry, and updates the database-first refactor note so the docs no longer describe an agent-local DB as current runtime surface.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm docs:list`\n- `pnpm deadcode:unused-files`\n- `pnpm deadcode:dependencies`\n- `pnpm db:kysely:check`\n- `pnpm lint:kysely`\n- `git diff --cached --check`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local` (clean; no accepted/actionable findings)\n",
